headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Freeport-McMoRan (FCX) After A 75% One-Year Rally?
summary: If you have been wondering whether Freeport-McMoRan is still attractively priced after its strong run, this article will help you weigh what the current share price might be implying. The stock last closed at US$65.46, with returns of 5.8% over 7 days, 11.5% over 30 days, 26.1% year to date, 74.8% over 1 year, 61.3% over 3 years, and 105.3% over 5 years.
